WEBVTT

01:57.280 --> 01:58.800
I didn't expect you to come.

02:03.360 --> 02:04.360
I didn't either.

02:06.320 --> 02:10.880
You came to ask who you really are,

02:11.600 --> 02:12.440
right?

02:15.160 --> 02:16.000
No.

02:17.520 --> 02:18.720
I came to find you

02:19.760 --> 02:20.760
to ask

02:23.760 --> 02:24.960
where Wu Wangyan is.

02:28.280 --> 02:29.600
Even this Moon Summoning Pearl
can't find her.

02:31.320 --> 02:32.920
Look at this Shilin Sect.

02:35.320 --> 02:36.400
Over a thousand years,

02:38.440 --> 02:40.560
there are too many power seals here.

02:41.080 --> 02:42.480
Even I can't undo them.

02:43.360 --> 02:44.200
And the Formless Moon

02:44.800 --> 02:47.480
has existed since Nuwa's time.

02:52.000 --> 02:55.080
<i>There are also</i>
<i>too many ancient seals there.</i>

02:55.960 --> 02:59.400
A tiny Moon Summoning Pearl
could hardly do anything.

03:08.760 --> 03:09.760
Greetings, Master Chi Wen.

03:22.800 --> 03:23.920
What's wrong?

03:24.880 --> 03:26.000
To our surprise, inside the Shilin Sect,

03:26.640 --> 03:28.200
there is a fragment of Jiu Ying's spirit.

03:29.640 --> 03:32.920
And it's hidden on one of us.

04:20.320 --> 04:21.200
So it's you!

04:30.160 --> 04:33.240
You must know
what I want to discuss with you.

04:34.120 --> 04:35.080
Yes.

04:36.320 --> 04:37.320
This secret

04:38.760 --> 04:41.120
has long been kept in my heart.

04:45.480 --> 04:47.440
You were afraid
the other members would find out,

04:48.160 --> 04:50.000
so you asked to see me alone.

04:51.000 --> 04:52.400
Stop pretending, Jiu Ying.

04:54.640 --> 04:56.840
Stop defiling her merciful face.

05:06.800 --> 05:10.600
You are braver than I thought.

05:12.440 --> 05:14.600
If I really carry
a fragment of Jiu Ying's spirit,

05:15.240 --> 05:17.000
then doesn't that mean…

05:18.520 --> 05:19.840
Jiu Ying knows everything about me?

05:36.320 --> 05:39.720
Bai Ze's Eastern Purple Lightning
can suppress evil spirits.

05:40.640 --> 05:41.480
Wear it,

05:42.440 --> 05:44.640
and it can temporarily
suppress Jiu Ying's spirit.

06:16.080 --> 06:17.160
Thank you.

06:21.280 --> 06:22.320
Don't mention it.

06:25.520 --> 06:27.640
Aside from the two fragments
inside the Oracle Stone,

06:27.720 --> 06:31.880
we've gathered all 78 fragments
in this world.

06:32.840 --> 06:36.640
I didn't expect the one
that remained lost all this time

06:37.240 --> 06:38.360
would be on you.

06:38.440 --> 06:40.360
I'm going to the Formless Moon
to save someone.

06:40.440 --> 06:42.320
Maybe we can go together.

06:42.400 --> 06:45.400
We can destroy the last two fragments
in the Oracle Stone.

06:45.480 --> 06:49.080
The Oracle Stone is a sacred stone
created by Pan Gu and Nuwa together.

06:49.160 --> 06:51.840
Ordinary power can hardly damage it.

06:51.920 --> 06:53.840
Only by gathering the Dragon Deity's Power

06:54.360 --> 06:57.080
might there be a chance to destroy it.

06:59.000 --> 07:00.520
What about Wu Wangyan?

07:01.280 --> 07:02.120
I promise you.

07:03.120 --> 07:04.560
She will be saved.

07:05.760 --> 07:06.600
And

07:07.880 --> 07:09.160
Lu Wuyi is there too.

07:10.320 --> 07:12.280
We're about to enter the Sacred Spring.

07:12.800 --> 07:15.080
Why did the Queen summon Wangyan alone?

07:17.480 --> 07:18.320
Hui,

07:19.000 --> 07:21.240
you're the closest to Wangyan.

07:21.320 --> 07:22.720
Do you know what's going on?

07:25.480 --> 07:26.600
I don't know.

07:27.160 --> 07:28.000
Wangyan…

07:28.600 --> 07:30.280
didn't tell me anything.

07:52.760 --> 07:54.360
It may be out of your reach

07:55.880 --> 07:57.760
to deal with me.

08:00.400 --> 08:02.280
I've been wondering

08:03.040 --> 08:05.880
why your memories were always fragmented

08:06.640 --> 08:08.240
every time we entered the Sacred Spring.

08:09.480 --> 08:12.720
Turns out you suspected me all along

08:13.480 --> 08:16.680
and removed some memories
you didn't want me

08:16.760 --> 08:19.120
and your sisters to know.

08:19.720 --> 08:20.600
Right?

08:21.600 --> 08:22.560
Yes.

08:24.680 --> 08:29.120
But tonight, if I share
my memories with them,

08:29.960 --> 08:31.040
all of them will know

08:31.800 --> 08:34.159
that you are Jiu Ying.

08:36.440 --> 08:38.080
You won't get the chance.

08:50.600 --> 08:51.960
The Tenth Dragon Son

08:52.480 --> 08:55.720
can help you kill Chi Wen.

08:59.360 --> 09:00.880
You know too much.

09:02.120 --> 09:03.520
You deserve to die.

09:09.000 --> 09:10.640
Keep me alive…

09:11.920 --> 09:13.720
and I can help you.

09:14.320 --> 09:16.040
I am his weakness.

09:16.960 --> 09:19.880
He'll obey you for my sake…

09:19.960 --> 09:21.680
I need your help?

09:23.200 --> 09:24.480
Have you forgotten

09:26.160 --> 09:28.040
what I'm best at?

09:41.960 --> 09:43.720
When I wiped out the Flood Dragon clan,

09:44.240 --> 09:47.120
I transferred the spirit fragment in you

09:48.560 --> 09:50.800
<i>into Wu Shiguang's body.</i>

09:53.760 --> 09:54.800
No way…

09:55.800 --> 09:58.760
Then how did you appear
in the Oracle Stone?

09:59.520 --> 10:03.440
The Oracle Stone has three fragments.

10:05.360 --> 10:06.200
Back then,

10:06.280 --> 10:10.200
one fragment was used to control you
to slaughter the Flood Dragon clan.

10:10.840 --> 10:12.000
The rest remain

10:12.560 --> 10:14.360
in the Oracle Stone.

10:21.200 --> 10:23.160
You're right, though.

10:23.760 --> 10:27.720
Keeping you alive
can indeed be his weakness.

10:52.120 --> 10:53.120
No.

10:54.000 --> 10:56.200
Get close to Wu Shiguang.

10:56.960 --> 11:01.240
Try to get his prayer beads
and bring them to me.

11:06.400 --> 11:08.080
So you and the Dragon Deity

11:09.760 --> 11:11.640
have been plotting all along.

11:37.280 --> 11:40.600
I will find out the truth
and prove Wangyan hasn't betrayed us.

11:40.680 --> 11:41.680
Wangyan,

11:41.760 --> 11:45.080
why are you so fragrant today?

11:45.680 --> 11:48.480
You deceived Wangyan,
using her to do your work.

11:48.560 --> 11:50.280
What's your purpose exactly?

11:51.080 --> 11:53.680
<i>When we go back</i>
<i>and enter the Sacred Spring,</i>

11:53.760 --> 11:55.520
your plan with Wangyan

11:55.600 --> 11:57.040
will be known by the Queen.

11:57.120 --> 11:58.360
Without memory sharing,

11:59.120 --> 12:00.840
would you tell your Queen?

12:43.480 --> 12:44.440
Wangyan.

12:50.600 --> 12:53.600
Everything I said
to the Dragon Deity was a lie.

12:55.120 --> 12:56.840
I was just playing along

12:58.320 --> 13:01.040
to carry out the Queen's mission.

13:01.120 --> 13:02.080
Really?

13:17.000 --> 13:19.360
Greetings, Master.

13:35.680 --> 13:38.040
I'm sorry, Master.

13:41.560 --> 13:43.600
I ask to quit the Dragon-Slaying mission.

13:45.920 --> 13:46.880
See?

13:48.760 --> 13:52.560
The fated one can't escape fate after all.

13:54.240 --> 13:55.320
Master,

13:58.160 --> 13:59.560
what exactly does

14:02.240 --> 14:03.720
"fated one" mean?

14:05.120 --> 14:08.520
When the time comes, you'll understand.

14:11.640 --> 14:12.720
Where's Wangyan?

14:14.120 --> 14:15.240
Where did she go?

14:18.760 --> 14:20.120
She's…

14:21.880 --> 14:23.040
in quiet reflection.

14:33.440 --> 14:34.720
There's no moon tonight.

14:38.160 --> 14:41.200
The moon is always there,
just hiding for now.

14:44.000 --> 14:46.120
The other moons are all bright and clear.

14:46.760 --> 14:49.520
Poets write verses praising them.

14:50.480 --> 14:51.720
Do you think

14:53.720 --> 14:55.760
that moon no one can see

14:57.720 --> 14:59.280
would feel sad?

15:00.040 --> 15:01.800
What other moons?

15:03.600 --> 15:07.360
There is only one moon,
just in different phases.

15:07.440 --> 15:08.600
We…

15:09.720 --> 15:10.960
are one.

15:19.960 --> 15:20.880
Wangyan,

15:22.360 --> 15:23.760
if one day,

15:24.840 --> 15:26.560
no one can see me anymore,

15:28.120 --> 15:29.400
will you remember me?

15:29.920 --> 15:31.480
Silly,

15:33.440 --> 15:35.040
we'll be together forever.

16:30.640 --> 16:31.640
Wuyi,

16:32.640 --> 16:33.720
I'm sorry…

16:40.320 --> 16:41.240
I lied to you.

16:42.400 --> 16:43.320
No need to apologize.

16:46.960 --> 16:48.080
I lied to you too.

16:50.840 --> 16:52.640
The Queen had me watch you.

16:54.040 --> 16:55.600
I know about your partnership

16:56.920 --> 16:57.920
with Ji Ling.

17:04.319 --> 17:06.040
So you told the Queen?

17:12.760 --> 17:14.000
Do you hate me?

17:14.599 --> 17:15.440
No.

17:18.359 --> 17:19.839
I could never hate you.

17:24.359 --> 17:26.400
Aren't you going to ask why I'm here?

17:27.359 --> 17:28.880
If the Queen sent me to kill you,

17:29.760 --> 17:30.920
you wouldn't hate me?

17:36.360 --> 17:37.440
No.

17:38.800 --> 17:40.720
If I die by your hand,

17:41.840 --> 17:43.080
at least it wouldn't hurt.

18:01.760 --> 18:02.880
Wu Wangyan…

18:05.280 --> 18:06.960
What do you really want?

18:10.480 --> 18:11.560
I don't know.

18:13.440 --> 18:14.920
But I know

18:16.200 --> 18:17.360
what I don't want.

18:18.360 --> 18:19.640
Not even your life?

18:20.720 --> 18:22.160
Not even your own life?

18:34.480 --> 18:37.320
I don't want my hands
to be forever stained with blood.

18:39.080 --> 18:41.040
I don't want Jiu Ying
to keep controlling me,

18:41.960 --> 18:44.320
stirring up killing and hatred
in this world.

18:46.080 --> 18:47.880
I don't want to be a moon…

18:51.800 --> 18:53.880
that only lights up mass graves.

19:15.360 --> 19:16.320
Do it.

19:37.840 --> 19:39.720
Wuyi, what's wrong?

19:43.800 --> 19:44.880
Wangyan…

19:47.440 --> 19:49.360
I never told the Queen.

19:50.520 --> 19:52.360
I would never betray you.

19:53.320 --> 19:55.040
I came to ask you…

19:57.120 --> 19:58.560
if you still remember…

20:01.800 --> 20:03.960
the words you once said to me.

20:07.240 --> 20:08.280
I have never forgotten.

20:08.360 --> 20:12.800
Then why did you leave me behind
and go alone?

20:16.960 --> 20:18.320
Because this path…

20:21.000 --> 20:22.200
is too dangerous.

20:25.040 --> 20:26.480
I didn't want you to walk it.

20:28.080 --> 20:31.800
Because my enemy is too terrifying.

20:32.440 --> 20:33.960
So I couldn't tell you.

20:36.160 --> 20:37.640
The danger…

20:42.040 --> 20:43.440
the truth…

20:44.920 --> 20:46.200
even my guilt toward you…

20:48.440 --> 20:49.760
None of it could be said.

20:52.520 --> 20:53.520
Enemy?

20:55.880 --> 20:56.920
Danger?

20:58.160 --> 20:59.600
You mean…

21:00.880 --> 21:02.000
the Queen?

21:04.600 --> 21:05.640
The Queen…

21:07.080 --> 21:08.160
is Jiu Ying.

21:11.080 --> 21:12.480
When the real Queen passed,

21:13.480 --> 21:15.680
her power had faded.

21:16.720 --> 21:19.120
<i>We missed her so much,</i>

21:20.200 --> 21:24.200
<i>so when Jiu Ying wore her skin</i>
<i>and showed up,</i>

21:25.160 --> 21:30.320
<i>we deceived ourselves</i>
<i>into believing she had gained</i>

21:31.160 --> 21:33.840
<i>the power of endless rebirth like us.</i>

21:54.840 --> 21:55.960
<i>He impersonated the Queen,</i>

21:56.680 --> 21:58.840
<i>faking the Oracle Stone's prophecy,</i>

21:58.920 --> 22:02.000
ordering us to sow killing
and hatred in this world.

22:02.600 --> 22:05.000
He called it the balance of the world,

22:05.080 --> 22:07.320
and we believed it without question.

22:08.000 --> 22:09.800
But Xiaowei saw through him.

22:13.440 --> 22:14.360
Wangyan,

22:15.440 --> 22:18.080
she is no longer the kind Queen we knew.

22:18.880 --> 22:23.200
The Formless Moon is now filled
with only cruelty and slaughter.

22:25.120 --> 22:26.480
Let me go.

22:27.160 --> 22:30.360
You should find a way and escape too.

22:33.360 --> 22:34.280
<i>Xiaowei is a traitor.</i>

22:35.040 --> 22:38.320
Can her words be trusted?

22:38.840 --> 22:40.280
I am a traitor too.

22:41.200 --> 22:45.000
Then do you believe my words?

23:01.400 --> 23:02.640
Who dares trespass?

23:03.160 --> 23:04.880
Aren't you afraid of perishing?

23:06.560 --> 23:07.520
Dragon Deity?

23:08.920 --> 23:11.320
Since you know who I am,

23:12.320 --> 23:13.760
why don't you back off?

23:14.720 --> 23:16.600
The Formless Moon is beyond this world,

23:17.320 --> 23:19.160
not bound by its rules.

23:19.680 --> 23:22.480
We respect what you've done
for all living things,

23:23.240 --> 23:25.160
but that doesn't mean we obey you.

23:25.840 --> 23:28.400
Master Dragon Deity, please leave.

23:29.680 --> 23:30.800
Where is Wu Wangyan?

23:31.520 --> 23:32.960
-Let her out.
-How dare you!

23:33.040 --> 23:36.400
Moon spirit invoked,
your radiance eternal, arise!

24:10.240 --> 24:13.760
By the fox's call, lend me your souls!

24:19.520 --> 24:22.200
Formless Moon members, come forth.

24:36.000 --> 24:38.320
Kneel before me.

24:42.480 --> 24:43.920
Obey me.

24:51.880 --> 24:53.000
You guys go save them.

24:54.440 --> 24:55.320
I'll handle things here.

24:59.200 --> 25:00.160
Wu Wangyan?

25:00.840 --> 25:01.840
Wu Wangyan!

25:12.680 --> 25:16.240
I told you I would find you.

25:21.520 --> 25:23.760
How did you know
where the Formless Moon is?

25:24.360 --> 25:25.280
Chi Wen knows.

25:34.520 --> 25:35.440
He's here too?

25:36.840 --> 25:37.880
Yes.

25:43.800 --> 25:45.000
I want to know

25:46.360 --> 25:47.400
who I really am.

25:50.560 --> 25:51.720
Knowing who you can be

25:52.480 --> 25:55.600
is more important than that.

25:57.320 --> 26:00.680
All memories are paths you've walked,

26:01.320 --> 26:05.080
a burden not worth turning back
to walk again.

26:05.880 --> 26:08.680
Forward is the way to go.

26:09.640 --> 26:11.400
But if I don't know who I am,

26:13.600 --> 26:15.440
I don't know which way to go.

26:16.200 --> 26:19.760
If you really want to know it,
just go ask that butterfly demon.

26:21.320 --> 26:22.600
I'm teaching him reason,

26:23.120 --> 26:24.240
but you're teaching him
to break the rules!

26:25.200 --> 26:26.520
Master Chi Wen strictly forbids

26:27.120 --> 26:29.080
anyone to approach the butterfly demon.

26:30.280 --> 26:31.840
Why be so obedient?

26:31.920 --> 26:34.200
Li Jie, while Master is away,

26:34.280 --> 26:36.480
sneak in and find out.

26:37.000 --> 26:37.920
What do you say?

27:16.120 --> 27:20.280
Do you really think
you can easily take Wu Wangyan away?

27:22.280 --> 27:26.000
Do you really think
I'm here to save Wu Wangyan?

27:34.560 --> 27:36.280
Dragon hearts as one,

27:37.440 --> 27:38.640
all to source return,

27:40.400 --> 27:42.920
all barriers break!

27:56.400 --> 27:57.880
It worked!

28:31.400 --> 28:35.640
Even the Dragon Deity's Power
can't break Jiu Ying's seal.

28:38.160 --> 28:40.640
Jiu Ying has been absorbing
the Oracle Stone's power,

28:40.720 --> 28:41.680
growing stronger.

28:42.920 --> 28:45.800
And Wu Shiguang only has two pieces
of the Dragon Deity's Power.

28:46.320 --> 28:47.360
It's not enough.

28:50.880 --> 28:52.120
I also have one piece inside me.

28:54.280 --> 28:55.160
No!

28:55.240 --> 28:57.480
If you give it up, you'll die.

28:58.200 --> 28:59.880
Xiaowei and Wu Zhiqi died

28:59.960 --> 29:02.760
because Yuan Wuhuo
forcibly took their Dragon Deity's Power

29:03.280 --> 29:04.640
and damaged their spiritual veins.

29:05.400 --> 29:08.280
If I give mine willingly, I'll be fine.

29:09.160 --> 29:12.560
Master Chi Wen saved me with this power

29:13.560 --> 29:15.000
that was never mine.

29:15.800 --> 29:19.320
Returning it is only right.

29:21.720 --> 29:22.920
Dragon hearts as one,

29:23.440 --> 29:24.680
all to source return,

29:25.200 --> 29:26.960
all barriers break!

30:11.000 --> 30:12.440
From now on,

30:12.520 --> 30:15.160
you are neither demon nor human.

30:16.200 --> 30:18.920
In this world,
you will be a unique existence

30:19.440 --> 30:21.320
and also the loneliest of its kind.

30:22.480 --> 30:23.720
From this moment,

30:24.240 --> 30:29.080
you are Chi Wen,
the last Dragon Deity in this world.

30:29.600 --> 30:33.680
So how long must I deceive the world?

30:35.320 --> 30:38.440
Until the Dragon's tenth son
awakens as a true dragon,

30:38.960 --> 30:41.560
your duty will be done.

30:44.160 --> 30:47.640
I didn't come here to be your enemy,

30:48.560 --> 30:49.880
but to seek cooperation.

30:53.320 --> 30:54.640
Don't trust me?

30:55.800 --> 30:58.280
If I hadn't told you
about Wu Wangyan's betrayal

30:58.880 --> 31:00.640
and the Taotie artifact,

31:01.160 --> 31:04.880
you might still be dancing
in her palm even now.

31:05.720 --> 31:07.480
Since she has betrayed you,

31:08.000 --> 31:11.280
all her memories are stored
inside the Taotie artifact.

31:11.880 --> 31:12.960
If you don't believe me,

31:14.760 --> 31:16.160
you can see for yourself.

31:21.000 --> 31:22.960
Wu Wangyan is pitiful.

31:23.760 --> 31:25.800
She trusted you, helped you,

31:26.480 --> 31:29.800
but never knew
she was just a pawn in your game.

31:30.680 --> 31:33.760
For great goals, small costs are nothing.

31:35.000 --> 31:36.440
But you're pitiful too.

31:38.440 --> 31:40.800
You're just a pawn in Chi Wen's game.

31:41.880 --> 31:42.760
That's right.

31:45.080 --> 31:47.600
Chi Wen wants me
to wait for the tenth son,

31:48.400 --> 31:52.280
then hand over the Dragon Deity's throne
I worked so hard to build.

31:54.520 --> 31:56.640
All those centuries of suffering

31:58.640 --> 32:00.320
would be a joke then?

32:01.680 --> 32:02.520
So…

32:04.840 --> 32:08.160
Jiu Ying, we should work together.

32:08.800 --> 32:11.680
My goal aligns with yours,

32:13.200 --> 32:14.320
to slay the dragon deity.

32:16.560 --> 32:20.840
Even if Chi Wen dies,
there's still the tenth son.

32:22.120 --> 32:25.400
How could a false deity like you
ever take the throne?

32:28.960 --> 32:31.200
I intended to seize
the Dragon Deity's Power

32:31.280 --> 32:32.600
to stop Wu Shiguang from rising.

32:33.560 --> 32:35.440
But Yuan Wuhuo meddled,

32:35.960 --> 32:39.800
and things went awry,
unexpectedly helping Wu Shiguang.

32:41.040 --> 32:43.320
Since he's destined to be a dragon,

32:43.400 --> 32:45.080
let him do the slaying.

32:46.240 --> 32:47.200
Besides,

32:47.720 --> 32:51.000
doesn't this play right
into the self-protection

32:51.080 --> 32:53.640
they set up out of fear?

32:55.760 --> 32:57.400
Only the Dragon Deity's Power

32:58.040 --> 32:59.640
can kill a dragon deity.

33:01.680 --> 33:05.840
And that is such a grave crime

33:08.000 --> 33:11.560
that the slayer, too,
will be consumed by its curse.

33:13.360 --> 33:14.680
Then the throne

33:16.680 --> 33:18.480
will be mine forever.

33:25.280 --> 33:26.800
What are you waiting for?

33:26.880 --> 33:29.480
You've been trapped
in Chi Wen's broken body

33:30.040 --> 33:30.880
for so many years.

33:31.480 --> 33:34.600
You should know I didn't lie.

33:35.360 --> 33:36.200
Isn't that right?

33:37.320 --> 33:39.080
The Dragon's tenth son…

33:42.240 --> 33:44.800
Only the Dragon Deity's Power
can slay a dragon deity.

33:45.600 --> 33:48.480
So Jiu Ying will use the tenth son
to kill me,

33:49.000 --> 33:53.280
so his true form
can break free from my body.

33:56.720 --> 33:58.040
The Dragon's tenth son?

33:59.640 --> 34:00.880
Interesting.

34:04.880 --> 34:09.159
You also sent butterfly demons to seize
the tenth son from the Dragon Abyss.

34:14.159 --> 34:15.120
That's right.

34:28.719 --> 34:32.320
<i>That outer-world being, Xie Lingxi,</i>
<i>is indeed something.</i>

34:33.120 --> 34:35.960
<i>However, he's too confident.</i>

34:36.040 --> 34:38.800
<i>He thought hiding the son</i>
<i>among the flood dragons</i>

34:38.880 --> 34:42.440
<i>with scales and horns too</i>
<i>would be safe enough</i>

34:42.520 --> 34:43.840
<i>to protect him.</i>

34:45.040 --> 34:46.120
<i>Too bad.</i>

34:46.880 --> 34:48.960
<i>I still found the tenth son.</i>

34:50.800 --> 34:53.280
You had the Formless Moon
pose as the Shilin Sect

34:53.880 --> 34:55.679
and slaughtered the Flood Dragon clan,

34:56.199 --> 34:59.000
making Xie Lingxi suspicious
of the Shilin Sect,

34:59.920 --> 35:01.840
so he hid the son deeper.

35:02.600 --> 35:05.960
The tenth son vanished without a trace.

35:07.360 --> 35:08.520
Suspicion

35:09.880 --> 35:12.760
is the best weapon
against the human heart.

35:13.600 --> 35:16.400
The Shilin Sect
had no news of the tenth son,

35:17.160 --> 35:20.120
but I always knew where he was.

35:20.720 --> 35:24.000
That's because you planted
a fragment of spirit inside him.

35:25.920 --> 35:29.920
But Wu Shiguang has grown up,

35:30.000 --> 35:32.840
yet he hasn't become a dragon,
which made me suspicious.

35:33.360 --> 35:34.200
So,

35:35.080 --> 35:36.640
you sent the Six-Eyed Butterfly.

35:39.360 --> 35:40.400
Yes.

35:41.800 --> 35:43.560
I had him devour a person

35:45.920 --> 35:47.800
to obtain his consciousness and memories.

36:05.320 --> 36:06.160
I knew…

36:09.560 --> 36:10.960
you would come.

36:12.040 --> 36:15.800
Tell me, who exactly are you?

36:17.600 --> 36:18.920
I am you.

36:22.560 --> 36:23.360
<i>And that person</i>

36:24.720 --> 36:26.600
<i>was the former hunter commander</i>
<i>of the Shilin Sect,</i>

36:26.680 --> 36:29.400
<i>plagued by the Wasting Sickness</i>

36:29.480 --> 36:31.440
<i>and long missing,</i>

36:33.280 --> 36:34.440
<i>Yuan Wuhuo.</i>

36:45.440 --> 36:46.840
You should be familiar with him.

36:50.440 --> 36:52.600
When I found Yuan Wuhuo,

36:53.400 --> 36:58.080
he was a decaying man
waiting to die alone in a cave.

37:00.720 --> 37:04.320
<i>Aging, gravely wounded beasts</i>

37:04.400 --> 37:07.800
<i>will all, in their final moments,</i>

37:07.880 --> 37:11.640
<i>go alone into hidden forests</i>
<i>or deep caves.</i>

37:13.040 --> 37:16.640
<i>They don't want their own kind</i>
<i>to witness their death.</i>

37:18.040 --> 37:21.960
<i>That is their final pride.</i>

39:34.840 --> 39:36.600
SERVE THE SCALES, UPHOLD THE RIGHT

39:39.400 --> 39:41.720
<i>Who are you? Where are you from?</i>

39:44.040 --> 39:45.040
<i>I don't remember.</i>

39:46.360 --> 39:47.680
What do you remember?

39:49.760 --> 39:50.680
It seems…

39:52.320 --> 39:53.960
<i>I have a younger brother.</i>

39:55.680 --> 39:56.520
<i>It seems…</i>

39:58.320 --> 39:59.720
<i>I need to find him.</i>

40:25.680 --> 40:29.200
To my surprise,
it took the Six-Eyed Butterfly decades

40:29.280 --> 40:31.920
to fully consume the consciousness
and memories of Yuan Wuhuo.

40:33.040 --> 40:36.400
His will was unyielding,
rare in this world.

40:38.080 --> 40:40.000
He truly was a stubborn man.

40:41.160 --> 40:44.080
Even the most stubborn one
can't outlast time.

40:45.360 --> 40:49.560
The mortal lifespan
is their greatest shackle.

40:50.720 --> 40:52.600
Yuan Wuhuo is no more.

40:53.720 --> 40:54.840
After that,

40:55.440 --> 40:59.760
the Six-Eyed Butterfly
roamed the world in his form.

41:01.560 --> 41:04.200
When the Six-Eyed Butterfly
returned to your side,

41:04.800 --> 41:07.000
you learned of the tenth son's secret.

41:07.840 --> 41:09.240
It's coming soon.

41:09.760 --> 41:14.240
Master Chi Wen entrusted the tenth son
to a very capable person to raise.

41:14.960 --> 41:18.120
When he comes of age, he will come to you.

41:18.920 --> 41:22.360
When he comes of age,
will he become a dragon?

41:23.760 --> 41:25.720
Like Master Chi Wen,

41:26.560 --> 41:29.720
majestic and powerful,
soaring through the heavens?

41:30.600 --> 41:32.480
The tenth son is special.

41:33.120 --> 41:35.960
He was created from nine reverse scales.

41:36.040 --> 41:38.160
He needs four pieces
of the Dragon Deity's Power

41:38.240 --> 41:40.000
to awaken and become a dragon.

41:40.080 --> 41:41.520
First, his scales form.

41:42.400 --> 41:43.640
Second, his claws grow.

41:44.480 --> 41:46.040
Third, his horns sprout.

41:47.600 --> 41:48.880
Fourth, his eyes ignite.

41:49.880 --> 41:51.760
You were eager to obtain
the Dragon Deity's Power

41:51.840 --> 41:54.040
to enter Wu Shiguang's body,

41:54.120 --> 41:56.920
so you used the fragment of spirit
planted within him.

41:57.440 --> 41:58.320
And subtly,

41:58.840 --> 42:02.240
you gave him hints,
leading him to Luo'an City.

42:03.120 --> 42:04.360
Every step after that,

42:05.240 --> 42:09.240
it's hard to say
whether it was Wu Shiguang's own will

42:10.120 --> 42:11.960
or your influence driving him.

42:14.240 --> 42:15.880
Everything you said is correct.

42:16.480 --> 42:20.040
But for your spirit fragment
to fully control him,

42:20.960 --> 42:23.880
you still need to find
the dark sides in his heart.

42:25.880 --> 42:28.360
Wu Shiguang is not weak-willed.

42:29.480 --> 42:31.080
After possessing him for so long,

42:31.960 --> 42:34.160
you've never found a way
to break his will.

42:35.960 --> 42:37.280
Not before,

42:38.840 --> 42:39.960
but now I have.

42:41.440 --> 42:42.480
You mean Wu Wangyan?

42:46.000 --> 42:52.440
Nothing breaks a person's spirit
more than losing what they love most.

42:53.400 --> 42:54.560
After all these years,

42:55.400 --> 42:57.960
you still don't understand
the human heart enough.

42:59.240 --> 43:02.520
Wu Shiguang already knows about her role
in slaughtering the Flood Dragon clan.

43:03.040 --> 43:04.440
His feelings for her now are complex.

43:05.400 --> 43:08.600
If you kill her now, it will only make him

43:08.680 --> 43:11.720
more determined to fight against you.

43:14.320 --> 43:15.920
You have a better idea?

43:17.400 --> 43:18.920
Let him rescue Wu Wangyan,

43:19.760 --> 43:22.360
let them rekindle their bond,
let their feelings grow deeper.

43:22.960 --> 43:24.880
Once he gathers
all the Dragon Deity's Power

43:24.960 --> 43:26.560
and his love for her runs deep,

43:27.320 --> 43:29.240
I'll kill Wu Wangyan before his eyes.

43:32.040 --> 43:33.720
He'll surely break down then.

43:42.720 --> 43:44.560
<i>You can take the chance</i>

43:44.640 --> 43:46.400
to seize his body.

43:47.320 --> 43:48.840
Then go to the Dragon Abyss,

43:49.360 --> 43:54.760
kill Chi Wen, and free your true form
from within his body.

43:57.000 --> 43:58.120
What do you think?

43:59.920 --> 44:00.960
And you?

44:04.200 --> 44:05.280
What do you want?

44:11.840 --> 44:14.080
I want to remain the Dragon Deity.
